title: 221. Andy & DJ CTI: Stephen Breyer To Retire, Antonio Brown Lawsuit & Threats From Russia
itunes:title: 221. Andy & DJ CTI: Stephen Breyer To Retire, Antonio Brown Lawsuit & Threats From Russia
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Justice Stephen Breyer retiring from the SCOTUS, Antonio Brown considering a defamation lawsuit against the Buccaneers, and Russia threatening to take 'appropriate measures' if the West's responses to demands aren't constructive.
